{"tha-ap72:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap72:0.2":"Sakacintaniyavagga ","tha-ap72:0.3":"Pupphacankotiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap72:1.1":"“Abhitarupam sihamva, ","tha-ap72:1.2":"garulaggamva pakkhinam; ","tha-ap72:1.3":"Byagghusabhamva pavaram, ","tha-ap72:1.4":"abhijatamva kesarim. ","tha-ap72:2.1":"Sikhim tilokasaranam, ","tha-ap72:2.2":"anejam aparajitam; ","tha-ap72:2.3":"Nisinnam samananaggam, ","tha-ap72:2.4":"bhikkhusanghapurakkhatam. ","tha-ap72:3.1":"Cankotake thapetvana, ","tha-ap72:3.2":"anojam pupphamuttamam; ","tha-ap72:3.3":"Saha cankotakeneva, ","tha-ap72:3.4":"buddhasettham samokirim. ","tha-ap72:4.1":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap72:4.2":"dvipadinda narasabha; ","tha-ap72:4.3":"Pattomhi acalam thanam, ","tha-ap72:4.4":"hitva jayaparajayam. ","tha-ap72:5.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap72:5.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap72:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap72:5.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap72:6.1":"Sampunne timsakappamhi, ","tha-ap72:6.2":"devabhutisanamaka; ","tha-ap72:6.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap72:6.4":"pancasum cakkavattino. ","tha-ap72:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap72:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap72:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap72:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pupphacankotiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap72:9.1":"Pupphacankotiyattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap72:10.1":"Sakacintaniyavaggo sattamo. ","tha-ap72:11.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap72:12.1":"Sakacinti avopupphi, ","tha-ap72:12.2":"sapaccagamanena ca; ","tha-ap72:12.3":"Parappasadi bhisado, ","tha-ap72:12.4":"sucinti vatthadayako. ","tha-ap72:13.1":"Ambadayi ca sumano, ","tha-ap72:13.2":"pupphacankotakipi ca; ","tha-ap72:13.3":"Gathekasattati vutta, ","tha-ap72:13.4":"ganita atthadassibhi. "}